### 9.4.4 Drag-and-Drop Behavior

```
User Action                     System Response
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
1. Hover over PM block         → Block highlights
                               → Cursor: grab

2. Start drag                  → Constraint window appears (blue band)
                               → Other PMs fade to 50% opacity

3. Drag within window          → Preview follows cursor
                               → Outline: GREEN
                               → Tooltip: "Valid: Feb 20"

4. Drag outside window         → Preview follows cursor
                               → Outline: RED
                               → Tooltip: "Violation: Outside compliance window"

5. Release (valid)             → Block moves to new position
                               → Projections recalculate
                               → Toast: "C2 moved to Feb 20"

6. Release (invalid)           → Block snaps back
                               → Toast: "Cannot schedule outside compliance window"
```

